 {
  "text": "Fernando, I am not a doctor. What does the Oncology Network do?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_fernando_i_am_not_a_doctor_what_does_the_oncolog.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "We provide cancer treatment to patients in many cities. The hospital offers a full network of care.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_we_provide_cancer_treatment_to_patients_in_many.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "How does the process work?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_how_does_the_process_work.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "First, the patient arrives. Then, our doctors develop a plan. Next, we provide the care.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_first_the_patient_arrives_then_our_doctors_devel.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "And the new therapies?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_and_the_new_therapies.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "We develop new treatments every year. They improve the results, and many patients get a cure.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_we_develop_new_treatments_every_year_they_improv.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Impressive. Does the cost go down too?",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_impressive_does_the_cost_go_down_too.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Yes. A bigger network improves the service and lowers the cost for patients.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a3_yes_a_bigger_network_improves_the_service_and_lo.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "We provide treatment to many patients.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a3_we_provide_treatment_to_many_patients.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "First the patient arrives, then we develop a plan.",
  "voice": "arthur",
